{"tid":1357353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「連登已死」唔撚再洗討論啦！ 已經無咗個種 你有道理 就可以上熱門 咁仲點愈辯愈明？","createTime":"2019-07-23T16:51:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T17:09:29.000Z","uid":7971,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9c516bd19d07c7f8458cfb99dcfb9365eac4470a","tid":1357353,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:51:38.000Z","msg":"//上環天橋開槍有片，推上熱門！！！ 文宣文宣文宣！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1357018//\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1357018//</a><br />\n我依個post 推左1個鐘 <br />\n都有接近900 like <br />\n但因為要推post 頁頁都只係推推推<br />\n咁討論啲咩啊？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔好叫「連登討論區」<br />\n叫「連登推post區」「連登風向區」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前一個post 推兩頁 就可以引發討論<br />\n有point嘅 就會多人討論 一齊傾先有行動 方向<br />\n<br />\n依家？<br />\n頁頁都係推推推 都上唔到熱門一<br />\n咁點討論啊？<br />\n仲要頁頁都只係回覆 推推推<br />\n咁仲係做到討論效果？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無咗個種 你有道理 就可以上熱門</span></span><br />\n咁係非常危險！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只要有網軍 打手<br />\n同一時間集中推一個post <br />\n就可以制造風向</span></span><br />\n依個問題一定要解決！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n/<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">Admin請入一入黎，依家根本討論唔到！已經無咗你有道理 就可以上熱門</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1357241\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1357241</a><br />\n<br />\n見到嘅巴打 入依個post 一齊傾 一齊俾意見<br />\n唔好寫推 都唔寫推<br />\n我哋要嘅係討論 同admin 一齊諗方法<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">守住連登 守住依場運動！</span></span>"},{"pid":"3b090d597fd5493db2ec2bd4645542ce36c2f486","tid":1357353,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:51:50.000Z","msg":"推自己"},{"pid":"3b1063f353936e4e247d49e5bf9850d33294b3bf","tid":1357353,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:52:17.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"c10e38cade5a5e14bd035687c6d796589a4b7862","tid":